headline: City of Rochelle, IL Expands Rochelle Intermodal Transload Center
summary: Today, representatives from the City of Rochelle, IL, along with state transportation officials, local economic partners, railroad, and trucking industries, celebrated the expansion of the City of Rochelle Intermodal Transload Center (RITC).

headline: Are Wall Street Analysts Bullish on Union Pacific Stock?
summary: Although Union Pacific has underperformed the broader market over the past year, Wall Street analysts maintain a moderately optimistic outlook about the stock’s prospects.

headline: M&A Transactions In July Included Largest Deal Of 2025
summary: M&A deals announced worldwide in July included a rail merger, which is the largest transaction in the past 12 months based on transaction value. Read more here.
